      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex-center flex-column py-4 mb-3">
    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading col-12 col-md-5 d-flex flex-column mb-3 py-4 order-md-2">Enfin, voici ce que l'aléatoire signifie réellement.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Découvre <a href="#">ici</a> une carte aléatoire à chaque clique, un vrai délice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 py-3 order-md-1">
        <img src="https://images.ctfassets.net/s5n2t79q9icq/5KboeIJo4mtR2Nnl5Vo3tP/c68e2c0ae60a05c29c62a1128094b33c/h8jufreglzu3.png?fm=avif" alt="Carrousel slide 3" class="d-block w-100 rounded">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div><!-- End THE FEATURETTES -->

<hr class="featurette-divider py-4">

<!-- ======= Carousel ======= -->
<div class="container">
  <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
    <!-- Indicators -->
    <div class="carousel-indicators">
      <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-label="Slide 1" aria-current="true"></button>
      <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2" class=""></button>
      <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3" class=""></button>
    </div>
    <!-- Carrousel -->
    <div class="carousel-inner rounded">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img src="https://images.hdqwalls.com/download/magic-the-gathering-the-prismatic-bridge-4k-fa-1920x1080.jpg" alt="Carrousel slide 1" class="d-block w-100">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption text-start">
            <h2>« La vie et la mort sont toutes deux réversibles. »</h2>
            <p>—Nicol Bolas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="https://images.hdqwalls.com/download/magic-the-gathering-1920x1080.jpg" alt="Carrousel slide 2" class="d-block w-100">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h2>« Une récompense qui en vaut la peine ne s'obtient jamais facilement. »</h2>
            <p>—Nicol Bolas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="https://images.hdqwalls.com/download/magic-the-gathering-gothic-4k-g4-1920x1080.jpg" alt="Carrousel slide 3" class="d-block w-100">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption text-start">
            <h2>« Les innocents paient-ils pour les coupables ? Bien entendu. Tel est le destin des faibles. »</h2>
            <p>—Nicol Bolas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Controls -->
    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </button>
    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</div><!-- End Carousel -->